title: My Mom Decides If We Can Get Married
description:
Lauren's Mom asks some majorly personal and uncomfortable questions... ie. does Jeremy know if he wants to marry Lauren? She puts them through a rigorous compatibility test based on the questions she thinks are important for a healthy and stable relationship. Do they pass the MomDIY couples test?
